  "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
  "body": "*Title*: ext_authz: Pass full downstream certificate to the external service\r\n\r\n*Description*:\r\nThis is a feature request.\r\n\r\nToday the ext_authz filter sends the principle of the downstream X.509 certificate in the [Peer AttributeContext](\r\nhttps://www.envoyproxy.io/docs/envoy/v1.11.1/api-v2/service/auth/v2/attribute_context.proto#service-auth-v2-attributecontext-peer).\r\n\r\nIn our authorization system we require validation of additional parts of the X.509 certificate.\r\n\r\nWe propose to send the full downstream client X.509 certificate as a label in the source Peer AttributeContext.",
